      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable daily driver that's built to last! This vehicle is a solid, honest performer that has been well-loved over the years. While it shows some typical signs of wear and tear both inside and out, it remains a reliable choice for anyone looking for a functional car at a great price. It's the perfect companion for your commute or weekend errands!",
