    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly pristine, mint condition, having been meticulously cared for and stored in a climate-controlled environment. The paint retains its original showroom luster with no visible imperfections, and the interior remains immaculate with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is flawless, with all systems functioning exactly as they did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been maintained to the highest possible standard.",
