      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the zenith of automotive preservation. Every aspect of this specimen, from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous stewardship and uncompromising care. It delivers a refined driving experience that remains indistinguishable from its original manufacture. For the discerning buyer seeking an investment-grade vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned market, this offering stands as a definitive benchmark of excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
